1
00:01:29,650 --> 00:01:33,039
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:36,220
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,770
Welcome, Tower Master.

4
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:46,759
I, Zan Hua, pay my respects to you.

5
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:51,960
Tower Master, why are you doing this?

6
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,690
You have the nerve to ask me?

7
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:56,150
I told you to keep an eye on Kou Wan.

8
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:59,120
I didn't expect you to be bewitched by her

9
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:02,160
and even join hands with her
to deceive me.

10
00:02:02,310 --> 00:02:05,680
If I hadn't discovered
that the gold coins were adulterated,

11
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,139
how long did you intend
to keep deceiving me?

12
00:02:15,990 --> 00:02:19,890
♪ Embroidered silk robe
wet with tear stains ♪

13
00:02:20,990 --> 00:02:25,040
♪ Last night in dreams,
I called your name once more ♪

14
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:30,550
♪ Cold moonlight fills the little tower,
the person has aged first ♪

15
00:02:31,730 --> 00:02:35,860
♪ When red beans ripened,
you paid no heed ♪

16
00:02:36,890 --> 00:02:41,380
♪ My hair flies as the wind blows ♪

17
00:02:42,579 --> 00:02:46,800
♪ Empty mountains, evening snow—
dim as a painting ♪

18
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:52,050
♪ This scene is hard to forget ♪

19
00:02:53,050 --> 00:02:59,040
♪ One life, one dream,
sharing endless sorrow ♪

20
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:08,730
Tower Master.

21
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:10,950
You're still calling me Tower Master.

22
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,480
Many years ago,

23
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:18,760
thank you
for killing Xie Quan and Ru Yue for me.

24
00:03:18,790 --> 00:03:19,829
Otherwise,

25
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,800
I would have died in the streets long ago.

26
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,100
I don't know how

27
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:25,800
I can repay such a great favor.

28
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:32,120
These adulterated gold coins—

29
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,920
is this how you repay me?

30
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:38,400
I've never intended to disobey you.

31
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,040
It's just that
I can't bear to see these noble people

32
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,920
treat human lives as their amusement

33
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,579
or profit from living beings.

34
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:45,340
I had no choice

35
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,920
but to do that.

36
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:48,460
Tell me,

37
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:52,360
where is the rest of the gold?

38
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,160
For the sake of our past,

39
00:03:57,079 --> 00:03:58,829
I will give you a quick death.

40
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,850
I know I can't escape death.

41
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:07,200
I am at your disposal, Tower Master.

42
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:12,320
You still won't talk.

43
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,270
Bring him in!

44
00:04:20,779 --> 00:04:21,579
Tower Master!

45
00:04:21,810 --> 00:04:23,520
This has nothing to do with him!

46
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,980
It was all done by me alone!

47
00:04:24,980 --> 00:04:26,240
Please, Tower Master,

48
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,840
don't kill the innocent.

49
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,850
I'll ask you one more time.

50
00:04:31,150 --> 00:04:33,220
Where is my gold?

51
00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:43,470
I don't know.

52
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:57,900
In that case,

53
00:05:00,140 --> 00:05:02,140
I will give you one last chance.

54
00:05:04,220 --> 00:05:05,330
Kill her,

55
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:09,080
and I will be lenient with you.

56
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:51,610
Sweet words are rarely sincere.

57
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:55,760
In a fickle world,
scheming politicians abound.

58
00:05:59,020 --> 00:06:00,390
I don't blame you.

59
00:06:04,540 --> 00:06:05,500
Do it.

60
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:33,220
You have lived such a hard life.

61
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,260
How could I have the heart

62
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:37,200
to let you leave alone?

63
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:43,909
Zan.

64
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:46,710
I remember you said before

65
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:49,250
that if one is unfaithful

66
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,680
and drags out an ignoble existence,

67
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:55,240
that's no different
from those filthy scums.

68
00:06:57,090 --> 00:06:58,050
Right?

69
00:07:10,490 --> 00:07:11,050
Zan!

70
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,270
Outrageous!

71
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,720
Do you both want to die?

72
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,880
Tower Master!

73
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,360
Your kindness in raising me—

74
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:25,960
I can only repay it in the next life.

75
00:07:26,390 --> 00:07:27,850
What are you going to do?

76
00:07:32,150 --> 00:07:33,040
Wan.

77
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:37,560
I've never heard you play the pipa before.

78
00:07:38,340 --> 00:07:39,690
When I heard it just now,

79
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,820
it was truly enchanting and moving,

80
00:07:43,850 --> 00:07:45,650
a heavenly sound without equal.

81
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:49,010
Being able to hear you
play a song in this life,

82
00:07:49,230 --> 00:07:50,590
I have no regrets.

83
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:02,640
Why are you so silly, Zan?

84
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,730
I will buy the best pipa.

85
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,380
Then I will return to the capital

86
00:09:13,380 --> 00:09:14,860
and reopen the Moon House.

87
00:09:14,890 --> 00:09:15,990
I will tell the world

88
00:09:15,990 --> 00:09:17,450
that Ms. Kou has returned.

89
00:09:17,810 --> 00:09:20,690
Hahaha.

90
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:23,030
What about you?

91
00:09:23,770 --> 00:09:26,090
What do you want to do after you get out?

92
00:09:30,260 --> 00:09:31,060
I don't know.

93
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:34,070
But...

94
00:09:35,740 --> 00:09:37,470
if you reopen the Moon House,

95
00:09:38,980 --> 00:09:40,840
I will surely be the first to come.

96
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:43,130
Then it's settled.

97
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,100
It's a deal.

98
00:09:57,710 --> 00:10:00,180
Did you know
about Kou Wan's matter or not?

99
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,990
Did you join hands with her to deceive me?

100
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,120
Do you think I can't find out
if you don't tell me?

101
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,920
Tower Master!

102
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,100
What?

103
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,330
You're finally willing to talk?

104
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:17,500
Do you know
what all these things you've done

105
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,920
are really for?

106
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,530
What do you mean?

107
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,680
Those noble people at the Lingya Tower—

108
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:24,230
no matter what amusement they want,

109
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:25,890
we do our best to satisfy them.

110
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:28,800
Yet they still only treat us as watchdogs.

111
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:30,720
Pat us on the head when we are useful.

112
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,380
Spit on us when we are useless!

113
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:35,050
How dare you say such treasonous words?

114
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:37,340
Do you know what punishment you deserve?

115
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:40,330
No matter how foolish or tyrannical,

116
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:41,960
the noble are always noble.

117
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,620
Because they were born noble!

118
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,760
Even if they become idiotic trash,

119
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:48,000
they can still trample upon us!

120
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:52,170
And no matter how well we do,

121
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,440
in their eyes,

122
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:58,000
they will never see us as human beings.

123
00:10:58,880 --> 00:10:59,680
Enough!

124
00:11:45,170 --> 00:11:46,620
I'm not sure,

125
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:48,770
but from your description,

126
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:50,400
that person should be her.

127
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:51,960
You know who Voice-Keeper Taiyin is?

128
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,980
I've never seen
what she looks like in person.

129
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:57,470
But before, Tower Master wanted
to transfer her to my level.

130
00:11:57,890 --> 00:12:00,490
Yet later, he changed his mind
for some reason.

131
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:01,880
That means...

132
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,200
she is on a higher level.

133
00:12:08,190 --> 00:12:10,390
I've finally reached the fourth level.

134
00:12:10,460 --> 00:12:12,940
I wonder how Master is doing now.

135
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,580
Here's some wound medicine.

136
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:37,050
Remember,

137
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:39,880
you are the daughter
of the Lingya Tower's master.

138
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:52,120
I am ashamed to have a father

139
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:54,640
like you.

140
00:13:04,430 --> 00:13:05,370
Thank you.

141
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:07,530
I didn't expect Ms. Kou to actually...

142
00:13:11,950 --> 00:13:13,670
Truly, good people die young.

143
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,800
Master and I
have killed so many people too.

144
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:23,720
Then do the two of us
count as good people or not?

145
00:13:31,590 --> 00:13:32,700
Tu Ya, stop.

146
00:13:36,610 --> 00:13:37,210
Jiang Man.

147
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,010
Man.

148
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:40,020
Are you crazy, Tu Ya?

149
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:49,990
Man,

150
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:51,680
what exactly happened?

151
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,580
How did you suddenly offend Tu Ya?

152
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:56,760
I just wanted to deliver some food to her
out of kindness.

153
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:57,960
I didn't know she would try to kill me.

154
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,480
Shut up!

155
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:04,040
I don't want anything touched by her.

156
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:06,530
If you want to live,
stay away from her too.

157
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:08,810
What's wrong with you?

158
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:10,810
Picking a fight here for no reason.

159
00:14:17,590 --> 00:14:19,640
Tu Ya, what do you mean?

160
00:14:19,670 --> 00:14:21,770
I hope you can explain clearly

161
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:23,510
in front of all of us.

162
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,280
Two years ago,

163
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,360
someone single-handedly

164
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:30,360
poisoned the entire Jiang Village.

165
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:32,880
I don't want to die an unnatural death.

